This project is an AI-powered portfolio website built using no-code tools to demonstrate how artificial intelligence can enhance modern web development without traditional programming. The website is designed for freelancers and interns to showcase their skills, projects, and experience in a professional and interactive way.

AI tools were used to assist in content generation, user interaction, and workflow automation. The website includes AI-generated content, an AI-style chatbot for visitor engagement, and automated contact handling to simulate real-world business use cases.

The project highlights how no-code platforms combined with AI can reduce development time while maintaining usability, responsiveness, and scalability.

